msgid ""
"Klein for Ray delivery guarantees across sources, checkpoints, state, "
"replay, and sinks."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 在源、检查点、状态、重放和 sink 各边界上的交付保证。"

msgid "Delivery and consistency guarantees"
msgstr "交付与一致性保证"

msgid ""
"End-to-end delivery is the composition of source progress, operator "
"state, Klein checkpoints, replay, and sink publication. The weakest "
"boundary in that chain determines what an application can observe after "
"failure."
msgstr "端到端交付由源进度、算子状态、Klein 检查点、重放和 sink 发布共同组成。该链条中最弱的边界决定应用在故障后能观察到什么。"

msgid ""
"Klein's general progress contract is **at-least-once**. Managed state is "
"restored consistently with checkpointed source positions, but an "
"arbitrary external sink may already have accepted output that is replayed"
" after recovery. Do not describe a job as exactly-once merely because it "
"enables checkpoints."
msgstr ""
"Klein 的一般进度契约是 **at-least-once**。托管状态会与检查点记录的源位置一致地恢复，但任意外部 sink "
"可能已经接收了恢复后会被重放的输出。不要仅仅因为作业启用了检查点，就将其描述为 exactly-once。"

msgid "Terms"
msgstr "术语"

msgid "**At-most-once** can lose records but does not deliberately replay them."
msgstr "**At-most-once** 可能丢失记录，但不会主动重放记录。"

msgid ""
"**At-least-once** does not lose records inside its stated recovery "
"boundary, but the same logical record may be processed or published more "
"than once."
msgstr "**At-least-once** 在其声明的恢复边界内不会丢失记录，但同一逻辑记录可能被处理或发布多次。"

msgid ""
"**Checkpoint-transactional visibility** keeps prepared sink output "
"private until checkpoint metadata is durable and makes commit retry "
"idempotent."
msgstr ""
"**Checkpoint-transactional visibility** 会将已准备的 sink "
"输出保持为私有，直到检查点元数据持久化，并使提交重试具备幂等性。"

msgid ""
"**Idempotent effect** means repeating an operation produces the same "
"external state. It is an application or connector property, not a synonym"
" for exactly-once processing."
msgstr ""
"**Idempotent effect** 表示重复执行某个操作会产生相同的外部状态。它是应用或连接器的属性，不等同于 exactly-once "
"处理。"

msgid "Source progress"
msgstr "源进度"

msgid "Source"
msgstr "源"

msgid "Recovery position"
msgstr "恢复位置"

msgid "Important boundary"
msgstr "重要边界"

msgid "Bounded Ray Data readers"
msgstr "有界 Ray Data reader"

msgid "Ray Data execution/retry state"
msgstr "Ray Data 执行/重试状态"

msgid "Klein streaming checkpoints do not govern a batch reader."
msgstr "Klein 流式检查点不管理批处理 reader。"

msgid "Finite collection source"
msgstr "有限集合源"

msgid "Source cursor in Klein checkpoint"
msgstr "Klein 检查点中的源游标"

msgid "Restore resumes from the checkpointed next record."
msgstr "恢复会从检查点记录的下一条记录继续。"

msgid "Continuous Kafka"
msgstr "连续 Kafka"

msgid "Per-topic/partition next offsets in Klein checkpoint"
msgstr "Klein 检查点中每个 topic/partition 的下一 offset"

msgid ""
"Group offsets are committed only after the corresponding Klein checkpoint"
" is durable."
msgstr "只有对应的 Klein 检查点持久化后，才提交 group offset。"

msgid "Canal JSON over Kafka"
msgstr "Kafka 上的 Canal JSON"

msgid "Kafka offsets plus the entire decoded FlatMessage"
msgstr "Kafka offset 加完整的已解码 FlatMessage"

msgid "A checkpoint cannot split recovery in the middle of one Kafka message."
msgstr "检查点不能在一条 Kafka 消息中间拆分恢复位置。"

msgid "RocketMQ"
msgstr "RocketMQ"

msgid "Broker-managed consumer-group progress"
msgstr "由 broker 管理的 consumer-group 进度"

msgid ""
"Broker acknowledgement can move ahead of the last durable Klein "
"checkpoint; a full job rollback may lose those messages."
msgstr "broker 确认可能领先于最近的持久 Klein 检查点；完整作业回滚可能丢失这些消息。"

msgid "Custom `SourceFunction`"
msgstr "自定义 `SourceFunction`"

msgid "Opaque value from `snapshot_state()`"
msgstr "来自 `snapshot_state()` 的不透明值"

msgid ""
"Correctness depends on capturing the next read position and implementing "
"idempotent `notify_checkpoint_complete()`."
msgstr "正确性取决于捕获下一读取位置，并以幂等方式实现 `notify_checkpoint_complete()`。"

msgid ""
"For a custom source, advance the local next-position state before calling"
" `SourceContext.collect()`. The checkpoint barrier emitted by that call "
"can then record the position corresponding to all preceding records."
msgstr ""
"对于自定义源，请在调用 `SourceContext.collect()` "
"前推进本地的下一位置状态。该调用发出的检查点屏障随后便能记录与此前所有记录对应的位置。"

msgid "Stateful operators and replay"
msgstr "有状态算子与重放"

msgid ""
"Checkpoint barriers align source positions, managed keyed state, timers, "
"operator watermarks, and prepared sink committables. A restored stateful "
"operator therefore sees the state that belongs to the restored input "
"position."
msgstr ""
"检查点屏障会对齐源位置、托管键控状态、定时器、算子水位线和已准备的 sink "
"committable。因此，恢复后的有状态算子会看到属于恢复输入位置的状态。"

msgid ""
"Klein derives checkpoint domains from weakly connected components of the "
"physical execution graph. One source threshold allocates a shared epoch "
"for all live sources in that domain; disconnected components progress "
"independently. Operators align that epoch by direct physical input and "
"hold post-barrier data and control messages on each arrived input until "
"the cut is complete. This avoids multiplying sink transactions by source "
"parallelism and prevents a multi-source sink state from being committed "
"with only one source position advanced."
msgstr ""
"Klein 根据物理执行图的弱连通分量推导检查点域。一个源阈值会为该域中的所有活动源分配共享 epoch；断开的分量独立推进。算子按直接物理输入对齐该 epoch，并在每个已收到屏障的输入上暂存屏障后的数据和控制消息，直至一致性切点完成。这样既不会按源并行度成倍增加 sink 事务，也能防止只推进一个源位置就提交多源 sink 状态。"

msgid ""
"The replay buffer retains emitted native-streaming batches until "
"downstream progress acknowledges them. It improves single-task recovery "
"and prevents an upstream task from forgetting data that a failed "
"downstream task had not made durable. Disabling `pipeline.replay-"
"buffer.enabled` changes the recovery path to a broader job restart; it "
"does not upgrade or downgrade an external sink's transaction semantics."
msgstr ""
"重放缓冲区会保留已发出的原生流式批次，直到下游进度确认它们。它能改善单任务恢复，并防止上游任务遗忘尚未由故障下游任务持久化的数据。禁用 "
"`pipeline.replay-buffer.enabled` 会将恢复路径改为更广泛的作业重启；它不会提升或降低外部 sink 的事务语义。"

msgid "Sink behavior"
msgstr "Sink 行为"

msgid "Sink"
msgstr "Sink"

msgid "Streaming guarantee"
msgstr "流处理保证"

msgid "Duplicate/loss guidance"
msgstr "重复/丢失指南"

msgid "Filesystem"
msgstr "文件系统"

msgid "Checkpoint-transactional visibility"
msgstr "Checkpoint-transactional visibility"

msgid ""
"Final part publication is idempotent. Readers must ignore `.klein-"
"staging`."
msgstr "最终分片发布具有幂等性。reader 必须忽略 `.klein-staging`。"

msgid "Iceberg append"
msgstr "Iceberg 追加"

msgid ""
"Parallel writers in one domain epoch are coalesced into one "
"append/snapshot; a stable transaction ID makes coordinator retries "
"idempotent while that snapshot is retained."
msgstr "同一域 epoch 内的并行 writer 会合并为一次 append/snapshot；只要该 snapshot 仍被保留，稳定的事务 ID 就能使协调器重试保持幂等。"

msgid "`TwoPhaseCommitSinkFunction`"
msgstr "`TwoPhaseCommitSinkFunction`"

msgid "Checkpoint-transactional when correctly implemented"
msgstr "正确实现时为 Checkpoint-transactional"

msgid ""
"`transaction_id` commit and abort operations must be idempotent across "
"retries."
msgstr "`transaction_id` 的提交和中止操作在重试之间必须具备幂等性。"

msgid "Kafka"
msgstr "Kafka"

msgid "At-least-once"
msgstr "At-least-once"

msgid ""
"Klein waits for delivery acknowledgements but does not use Kafka "
"transactions. Use a stable key/version or downstream deduplication."
msgstr "Klein 会等待交付确认，但不使用 Kafka 事务。请使用稳定的键/版本或下游去重。"

msgid "SQL"
msgstr "SQL"

msgid "Use an idempotent statement, unique key, or database-native upsert."
msgstr "使用幂等语句、唯一键或数据库原生 upsert。"

msgid "Redis"
msgstr "Redis"

msgid "At-least-once external effect"
msgstr "At-least-once 外部效果"

msgid ""
"Built-in replacement operations are idempotent for one key/value state, "
"but cross-key atomicity is not provided."
msgstr "内置替换操作对单个键/值状态具有幂等性，但不提供跨键原子性。"

msgid "Console"
msgstr "Console"

msgid "At-least-once diagnostic output"
msgstr "At-least-once 诊断输出"

msgid "Duplicate JSON Lines are expected after replay."
msgstr "重放后预期会出现重复的 JSON Lines。"

msgid "Custom `SinkFunction`"
msgstr "自定义 `SinkFunction`"

msgid "Connector-defined, normally at-least-once"
msgstr "由连接器定义，通常为 at-least-once"

msgid "`flush()` is a barrier boundary, not an external transaction by itself."
msgstr "`flush()` 是屏障边界，其本身不是外部事务。"

msgid "Ray Data writer"
msgstr "Ray Data writer"

msgid "Ray Data-defined"
msgstr "Ray Data-defined"

msgid ""
"Consult the selected Dataset writer; Klein streaming checkpoints are not "
"involved."
msgstr "请查阅所选 Dataset writer；Klein 流式检查点不参与其中。"

msgid "Failure-scenario checklist"
msgstr "故障场景检查清单"

msgid "Before production, test the following with the chosen source/sink pair:"
msgstr "投入生产前，请使用所选源/sink 组合测试以下场景："

msgid "Kill one transform worker while records are in flight."
msgstr "在记录仍处于传输途中时终止一个转换 worker。"

msgid ""
"Kill a sink worker after the external write but before checkpoint "
"completion."
msgstr "在完成外部写入之后、检查点完成之前终止一个 sink worker。"

msgid "Restart the coordinator after checkpoint metadata is written."
msgstr "写入检查点元数据后重启协调器。"

msgid "Stop the submitting driver while the detached job continues."
msgstr "在分离作业继续运行时停止提交作业的 driver。"

msgid "Recreate the job from a durable checkpoint after losing the whole cluster."
msgstr "整个集群丢失后，从持久检查点重新创建作业。"

msgid ""
"For every test, record the accepted loss and duplicate envelope, how a "
"duplicate is detected, and which identifier makes the external effect "
"idempotent. See [Restore and rescale a job](checkpoint-recovery.md) for "
"the recovery procedure and [Observe Klein jobs](observability.md) for the"
" relevant metrics."
msgstr ""
"对于每项测试，请记录可接受的丢失和重复范围、如何检测重复项，以及哪个标识符使外部效果具备幂等性。恢复流程请参阅 [恢复作业与调整作业规模"
"](checkpoint-recovery.md)，相关指标请参阅 [观测 Klein 作业](observability.md)。"
